* {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Ichikawa City)|ja|天満天神宮 (市川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} - A shrine located at the site of the former Ōno Castle in Ōnocho, Ichikawa City, Chiba Prefecture, and is an outer shrine of {{ill|Honkōji|ja|本光寺 (市川市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. It is not a religious corporation. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Minobu Town)|ja|天満天神宮 (身延町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Koseki, Minobu Town, Nanko District, Yamanashi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Shimada City)|ja|天満天神宮 (島田市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Itachi, Shimada City, Shizuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Nishiizu Town)|ja|天満天神宮 (西伊豆町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Naka, Nishiizu Town, Kamo District, Shizuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Ōzu City)|ja|天満天神宮 (大洲市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Narunouko, Ōzu City, Ehime Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Odate, Kochi City)|ja|天満天神宮 (高知市尾立)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Odate, Kochi City, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Fukuicho, Kochi City)|ja|天満天神宮 (高知市福井町)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Fukuicho, Kochi City, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Asai, Tosa City)|ja|天満天神宮 (土佐市浅井)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Asai, Tosa City, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Yōishi, Tosa City)|ja|天満天神宮 (土佐市用石)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Yōishi, Tosa City, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Inocho, Edagawa Ikedani)|ja|天満天神宮 (いの町枝川池ノ谷)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Ikeno, Edagawa, Inocho, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Inocho, Edagawa Fujigase)|ja|天満天神宮 (いの町枝川藤ヶ瀬)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Fujigase, Edagawa, Inocho, Kochi Prefecture. * {{ill|Tenman Tenjingu (Hidaka Village)|ja|天満天神宮 (日高村)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} – Located in Motomura, Hidaka Village, Takaoka District, Kochi Prefecture.
